description: Ten-day sentences are handed down to members of the Co-ordination Council for organising rallies.
title: Belarus protests: Two opposition figures jailed
title_page: Belarus protests: Two opposition figures jailed - BBC News
maintext: Former culture minister Pavel Latushko, another leading member of the council, was questioned for more than three hours but not arrested. One of Belarus's most famous figures internationally, Nobel Prize-winning author Svetlana Alexievich, is due to be questioned on Wednesday for her role on the council.
